<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA612_05_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema612_05_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema612_05.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema612_05_ih_0002 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="2_green" lang="y">각기둥의 전개도를 보고 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">전개도를 접었을 때 선분 ㄴㄷ과 맞닿는 선분을 고르세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_05_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
              <div class="boolean_wrap">
                <div>
                  <button class="button1" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button2" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button3" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button4" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button5" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button6" type="button" data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button class="button7" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button8" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button9" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button10" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">전개도를 접었을 때 선분 ㄴㄷ과 선분 ㅂㅁ이 서로 맞닿습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">전개도를 접었을 때 면 ㅈㅊㅇ과 만나는 면을 모두 고르세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_05_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
              <div class="boolean_wrap multiple">
                <div>
                  <button class="button1" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button class="button2" type="button" data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button class="button3" type="button" data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button class="button4" type="button" data-answer-single="true"></button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">면 ㅈㅊㅇ은 삼각기둥의 밑면이므로 전개도를 접었을 때 옆면과 만납니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
